    "description": "<p>Combining timeless glamour with a vanguard spirit, St. Regis Hotels &amp; Resorts is committed to delivering exquisite experiences at more than 50 luxury hotels and resorts in the best addresses around the world. Beginning with the debut of The St. Regis hotel in New York by John Jacob Astor IV at the dawn of the twentieth century, the brand has remained committed to an uncompromising level of bespoke and anticipatory service for all of its guests, delivered flawlessly by a team of gracious hosts that combine classic sophistication and modern sensibility, as well as our signature Butler Service. We invite you to explore careers at St. Regis. In joining St. Regis, you join a portfolio of brands with Marriott International.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Be</strong> where you can do your best work,<br>\n<strong>begin</strong>&nbsp;your purpose,&nbsp;<strong>belong</strong>&nbsp;to an amazing global<br>\nteam, and&nbsp;<strong>become</strong>&nbsp;the best version of you.</p>",
